general.gigTitle: be your angular developer for website and admin portals

sellerCard.description: I am a web and mobile app developer with more than 5 years of experience. I mostly worked on angular, angular material, typescript, javascript, flutter, and node js.

description.content:
Hi, If you need an angular developer, you are on the right gig.


I have extensive experience in web development specifically in angular. I have been working as a front-end angular developer for the last 6 years. Currently, I am working as a full-stack developer. I worked in healthcare, e-commerce, and fin-tech domains. I developed websites and admin portals in different technologies. I primarily worked on the following technologies


  • HTML5
  • CSS3
  • Angular 
  • Angular material
  • primeng
  • Javascript
  • Typescript
  • Node JS
  • Express JS


Services I provide:

  • Fully functional angular application.
  • PSD to angular components
  • Figma/Adobe XD to angular website
  • Fully functional admin portal with theming
  • Firebase integration
  • Fuse angular theme integration
  • PDF generation using jsPDF or pdfmake libraries
  • Twilio Integration


Why choose me?

  • Develop applications with customer needs
  • Pixel-perfect and responsive website design
  • Always use the latest technology
  • Cover all development phases from design to deployment


GitHub: https://github.com/faridullah1

I was communicating with several developers about my project. I was not pleased with their first impression. I was pleased with Farid Ullah immediately. His communication skills were very professional and polite. His level of details and documentational skills was amazing. He worked very well and communicated with me via Zoom to get the project complete. Job well done!!

I had the privilege of working with Farid on a complex project that involved multiple developers. Farid's exceptional skill set, talent, and attention to detail stood out throughout our entire app development. I would highly recommend him for any Angular-related work, whether as an integral part of your development team or for or any angular related gigs. Farid's expertise played a pivotal role in the project's success, and his commitment to excellence is truly commendable.

The team was highly professional and exceptionally understanding. The project was significant, requiring the establishment of a comprehensive solution. 

Despite our initially unclear requirements, Taimour provided invaluable assistance. There were occasions when we needed to modify certain requirements, and these changes were handled smoothly. We are extremely satisfied with the service provided.
It was a pleasure to work with Farid again. Great communication and high-quality delivery. He will think along with you regarding the impact that changes could have on your product!
